{"tid":505052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過撘車比人地身上嘅味搞到想嘔","createTime":"2017-12-20T17:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T17:23:10.000Z","uid":7302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1019f0c50308a141052907d49ffb0462538ea86e","tid":505052,"uid":7302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"頭先去完街坐巴士返屋企 <br />\n突然有個身上有好重邊爐味嘅小姐坐係我前面<br />\n咁開頭都無咩野 之後聞得耐就覺得有啲想嘔 好辛苦 <br />\n但係其他位又比人坐哂 唯有死頂到落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人有過相同經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461589c5093232501087eb329c04a82537db7fa7","tid":505052,"uid":17189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n見到你條毒撚都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0f7d7c10f5571d312b8f30bffa246b18431e52","tid":505052,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"所以如果我唔係揸車 唔會食雞煲 廢事臭親人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920aade231e5aa3022269a353268608212428dd8","tid":505052,"uid":101522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"一定係做飲食/廚房 佢地身上陣油煙味"},{"pid":"7a1189e188874f813660c77980764e59028d8629","tid":505052,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:11:18.000Z","msg":"有 橙皮吽到開始爛嗰種味<br />\nfeel到個阿姐鍾意用天然環保DIY嘢"},{"pid":"0e603045e8c7d3da3bde3f2e567575229eaccf0d","tid":505052,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"頭油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 加拿大味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148f9054e47fe35b3a247a4acb5a5f19082d9223","tid":505052,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"試過隔離個呀叔好大浸煙味<br />\n唔止想嘔 直頭有啲頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d04048edc32df80d17cc43cc24ae53c0998deb","tid":505052,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"宿味<br />\n<br />\n臭到無人敢坐佢隔黎"},{"pid":"83b5a7bc6b51538842aae3b0b2e8464cb05ebe6b","tid":505052,"uid":29523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"呢排朝早凍，中午熱，<br />\n班無自理能力既死毒撚，死都唔除佢件千層羽絨，一上車見佢成頭汗，焗到出撚晒頭油、面油，一坐底個陣酸臭味真係黃膽水都嘔埋出黎&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開左頭頂個風口諗住吹散陣味，d毒撚又覺得人歧視佢，扮晒凍咁不停拉件衫條鏈，結果陣味愈揚愈勁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係要立法罰鳩呢班無自理能力既人，唔好比佢地出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}